   <li>A letter stating reasons for  applying (up to 2 pages)</li>
   <li>At least two recent reference  letters, focusing on the candidate&rsquo;s academic work and research skills as well  as experience in working collaboratively</li>
 </ul>
 <p><strong>Information  about the position</strong></p>
<ul>
